I have used latest edition on text editing and image adding so on i recommend to use CK editor it's really great and has many functionality easy to install and use in django project.
Installations part
1.pip install django_ckeditor
2.go to settings.py add in Installed_Apps
3.go to the models.pi import CKeditor
4.Use ck editor in table attribute whichever u needed
Desc=models.RichTextField()

For more details search in Google CK editor 
